node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Blvck Paris on August 10, 2021 tagging @makersplaceco, and @decentraland_foundation. May be an image of bottle and indoor.

node.text:
RAFFLE LIVE NOW! 
To celebrate DARK MODE 02, our second NFT drop on @makersplaceco, join us in @Decentraland_Foundation via your desktop to preview the art ahead of tomorrow's drop. Make sure to enter the raffle by claiming your POAP to get a '1 of 10' Blvck Skull water bottle 💀

How to participate:
1. Create a MakersPlace account and connect your personal digital wallet.
2. Join MakersPlace gallery on Decentraland (Hit the link in bio).
2. In the gallery, claim your Proof of Attendance Protocol from the Vending Machine and explore the new Drop series.
Winner of the raffle will be announced in 48 hours.
